        <item>
          <title>Patrick Rodgers takes the lead at Torrey Pines as Scheffler and McIlroy falter</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Rodgers was at his best Saturday when golf's best were faltering on a tough day at Torrey Pines, playing mistake-free until dumping a gap wedge into the water on the par-5 18th for his only bogey. That gave him a 4-under 68 and a one-shot lead going into the final round.]]></description>
